## 2. Component Requirements

### 2.1 Essential Components (Must Have)

#### Data Display
| Component | Priority | Use Case |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| **Data Table** | Critical | Fleet status, maintenance schedules, audit logs |
| **Cards** | Critical | Train status cards, KPI summaries |
| **Badges/Tags** | Critical | RUC indicators (ACCELERATE/NOMINAL/DECELERATE), status |
| **Progress indicators** | High | Maintenance progress, capacity utilization |
| **Stat/Metric displays** | High | KPIs, dashboard metrics |
| **Timeline** | High | Maintenance history, audit trail |
| **Empty states** | Medium | No data scenarios |

#### Data Tables - Detailed Requirements
- Sorting (multi-column)
- Filtering (per column, global search)
- Pagination (server-side support)
- Row selection (single, multi)
- Column visibility toggle
- Column resizing
- Fixed/sticky headers
- Row expansion (nested details)
- Export capability (CSV, Excel)
- Virtualization for large datasets (1000+ rows)
- Cell formatting (numbers, dates, currency)
- Custom cell renderers

#### Forms & Inputs
| Component | Priority | Use Case |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| **Text input** | Critical | Search, filters, data entry |
| **Select/Dropdown** | Critical | Train selection, status filters |
| **Multi-select** | Critical | Batch operations, multiple train selection |
| **Date picker** | Critical | Schedule dates, date ranges |
| **Date range picker** | Critical | Report periods, planning horizons |
| **Number input** | High | KM values, thresholds |
| **File upload** | High | CSV import |
| **Textarea** | Medium | Override reasons, notes |
| **Checkbox/Radio** | Medium | Options, filters |
| **Switch/Toggle** | Medium | Feature toggles, boolean settings |
| **Slider** | Low | Threshold adjustments |

#### Navigation & Layout
| Component | Priority | Use Case |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| **Sidebar navigation** | Critical | Main app navigation |
| **Breadcrumbs** | High | Deep navigation paths |
| **Tabs** | High | Section switching (Strategic/Tactical/Operational) |
| **Accordion** | Medium | Collapsible sections |
| **Drawer/Sheet** | Medium | Detail panels, filters |
| **Modal/Dialog** | Critical | Confirmations, forms, overrides |
| **Command palette** | Low | Power user quick actions |

#### Feedback & Overlays
| Component | Priority | Use Case |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| **Toast/Notification** | Critical | Success/error messages |
| **Alert/Banner** | Critical | System warnings, drift alerts |
| **Loading spinner** | Critical | Async operations |
| **Skeleton loaders** | High | Content loading states |
| **Tooltip** | High | Help text, truncated content |
| **Popover** | Medium | Additional info, mini forms |
| **Confirmation dialog** | Critical | Destructive actions, overrides |

#### Charts & Visualization
| Component | Priority | Use Case |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| **Bar chart** | Critical | Man-hours per week, workload comparison |
| **Line chart** | Critical | Mileage trends, drift over time |
| **Area chart** | High | Capacity utilization over time |
| **Gantt chart** | Critical | Maintenance schedule visualization |
| **Heatmap** | Medium | Track utilization calendar |
| **Gauge/Radial** | Medium | SLA compliance, utilization % |
| **Sparklines** | Low | Inline trend indicators |

**Note:** Chart library is likely separate (Chart.js, Recharts, etc.), but UI library should integrate well.

### 2.2 Domain-Specific Components (Custom Build Expected)

These will need to be built on top of the UI library:
- Train status card (with RUC indicator)
- Maintenance timeline component
- Plan comparison view (diff visualization)
- Decision reasoning panel (XAI display)
- Capacity calendar (heatmap variant)
- Fleet overview grid

