## 4. Integration Requirements

### 4.1 Chart Library Integration
Must integrate cleanly with:
- Chart.js (current choice)
- Recharts (alternative)
- Or provide built-in charts

### 4.2 Form Management
Should work seamlessly with:
- React Hook Form
- Or provide comparable form solution
- Validation integration (Zod/TypeBox)

### 4.3 State Management
Should not conflict with:
- React Query/TanStack Query
- Custom state machine (@dm/toolkit)
- Zustand (if needed)

### 4.4 Routing
Must work with:
- Astro's routing
- View Transitions API

