## 5. Specific Feature Requirements

### 5.1 Data Table Deep Dive

The data table is the most critical component. Requirements:

```
Features Required:
├── Core
│   ├── Sorting (client + server)
│   ├── Filtering (faceted, global search)
│   ├── Pagination (client + server)
│   └── Column management (hide/show, reorder)
│
├── Selection
│   ├── Row selection (checkbox)
│   ├── Multi-select with shift-click
│   ├── Select all (page/all)
│   └── Selection state management
│
├── Display
│   ├── Fixed headers
│   ├── Fixed columns (first column)
│   ├── Row expansion
│   ├── Nested rows
│   ├── Custom cell renderers
│   └── Row actions menu
│
├── Performance
│   ├── Virtual scrolling (1000+ rows)
│   ├── Lazy loading
│   └── Efficient re-renders
│
└── Export
    ├── CSV export
    ├── Excel export
    └── Print-friendly view
```

### 5.2 Date Components

Date handling is complex due to planning horizons:

- Single date picker
- Date range picker (for report periods)
- Week picker (for planning)
- Month picker (for strategic view)
- Year picker (for 12-year horizon)
- Calendar view with data overlay (heatmap style)
- Timezone handling (Dubai = UTC+4)

### 5.3 Modal/Dialog System

Must support:
- Stacked modals (modal on modal)
- Drawer variant (side panel)
- Confirmation dialogs with reason input
- Form modals with validation
- Full-screen modal (for complex workflows)
- Escape/click-outside handling
- Focus trap

### 5.4 Notification System

Must support:
- Toast notifications (auto-dismiss)
- Persistent alerts (require acknowledgment)
- Action buttons in notifications
- Progress notifications (file upload)
- Notification center/history
- Priority levels (info, success, warning, error, critical)

