## 6. Anti-Requirements (What We Don't Need)

To avoid over-engineering, we explicitly don't need:

| Feature | Reason |
|---------|--------|
| E-commerce components | Not an e-commerce app |
| Social/messaging features | Not a social app |
| Marketing/landing pages | Enterprise app, not marketing |
| Complex animations | Professional, not playful |
| Drag-and-drop builder | Fixed UI, not customizable by users |
| Rich text editor | Simple text inputs suffice |
| Video/media players | No media content |
| Maps integration | No geographic visualization needed |

