## 9. Decision Framework

### 9.1 Quick Decision Matrix

| If you prioritize... | Consider... |
|---------------------|-------------|
| Maximum flexibility | Radix UI + TanStack Table + Tailwind |
| Speed of development | Mantine or Ant Design |
| Modern aesthetics | shadcn/ui or NextUI |
| Enterprise features | Ant Design or MUI |
| Smallest bundle | Radix UI (headless) |
| Best data tables | Mantine + TanStack Table |

### 9.2 Recommended Evaluation Process

1. **Shortlist** 3 libraries based on this document
2. **Build prototype** of the dashboard with each
3. **Compare** bundle size, DX, visual quality
4. **Decide** based on empirical evidence

